1
00:00:51,200 --> 00:00:53,880
This is my assistant, Penelope.

2
00:00:53,880 --> 00:00:56,240
Your assistant is a First Class passenger?

3
00:00:56,240 --> 00:00:57,040
Hello.

4
00:00:57,040 --> 00:00:59,040
Sky! Tid-Gift!

5
00:00:59,400 --> 00:01:00,680
It must be exclusive...

6
00:01:00,680 --> 00:01:02,000
It must be special.

7
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:05,520
Let's say goodbye from the cockpit.

8
00:01:05,520 --> 00:01:06,280
Hey, look!

9
00:01:06,280 --> 00:01:07,520
Our captain...

10
00:01:07,520 --> 00:01:09,280
our first officer...

11
00:01:09,360 --> 00:01:11,680
There are no pilots on this aircraft!

12
00:01:14,240 --> 00:01:15,440
This plane is about to crash!

13
00:01:15,440 --> 00:01:16,840
Ready! Go!

14
00:01:16,840 --> 00:01:17,800
One, two, three, go!

15
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:26,000
This way, please. This way.

16
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:29,640
Hey guys, let's see what I do in a day...

17
00:01:29,640 --> 00:01:31,720
at Glamorous Airlines.

18
00:01:31,720 --> 00:01:34,120
Suddenly, one of our friends
became an influencer of Thailand.

19
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:35,160
No.

20
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:37,120
What do you mean "no"?

21
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:39,480
I mean, she's not our friend anymore.

22
00:01:39,480 --> 00:01:41,360
She's got over two million new friends now.

23
00:01:41,360 --> 00:01:42,520
Just look at her.

24
00:01:42,520 --> 00:01:43,680
I'm so sad right now.

25
00:01:43,680 --> 00:01:46,120
Today is my last day.

26
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:47,440
It's so sad.

27
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:49,080
Welcome on board.

28
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:50,640
Please, this way.

29
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:50,920
Welcome.

30
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:53,000
I'll take over from here.

31
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:55,080
Welcome to Glamorous's First Class.

32
00:01:55,080 --> 00:01:56,880
I will be taking care of you.

33
00:01:56,880 --> 00:01:58,360
Excuse me...

34
00:01:58,360 --> 00:02:00,000
