35
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:00,920
It's Poupee.

36
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:01,640
Ms. Poupee, please have a seat.

37
00:02:01,640 --> 00:02:03,760
Just watch.
As soon as the camera's off,

38
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:05,360
she'll turn into
a completely different person.

39
00:02:05,360 --> 00:02:09,440
I have to get back to work now, guys.

40
00:02:11,040 --> 00:02:12,400
Thank you, Chai.

41
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:13,360
Hey!

42
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:15,600
Chaba, isn't this a bit much?

43
00:02:15,600 --> 00:02:17,000
I'm so sorry.

44
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:21,520
What?

45
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:25,520
Her name is Chaba.
You should definitely file a complaint.

46
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:26,480
That's good.

47
00:02:26,480 --> 00:02:27,480
Take a photo of her!

48
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,000
Hey!

49
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:39,320
This is my assistant.

50
00:02:39,320 --> 00:02:40,720
Huh?

51
00:02:40,720 --> 00:02:42,960
Her name is Penelope.

52
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:45,040
Penelope, say hello to my friends.

53
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:46,320
Sky and Tid-Gift.

54
00:02:46,320 --> 00:02:47,880
Hello.

55
00:02:47,880 --> 00:02:50,720
Hello, Sky, Tid-Gift, bitches!

56
00:02:50,720 --> 00:02:51,560
Whoa!

57
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:53,080
You don't have to add the last word.

58
00:02:53,080 --> 00:02:54,760
Just "Sky" and "Tid-Gift" is fine.

59
00:02:54,760 --> 00:02:56,440
We're all friends here.

60
00:02:56,440 --> 00:02:58,800
Sky, Tid-Gift, bitches!

61
00:02:58,800 --> 00:03:01,160
That's it.
You've already said it twice now.

62
00:03:01,160 --> 00:03:05,040
Wait, so your assistant
is a First Class passenger?

63
00:03:05,040 --> 00:03:09,040
we can't exactly fly Economy, can we?

64
00:03:10,320 --> 00:03:13,320
Penelope, let's take a photo!

65
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:17,840
What the hell is even happening?

66
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:36,440
Oh, we're having salad today?

67
00:03:36,440 --> 00:03:38,720
Don't touch Christopher!

68
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:42,200
Hey, I didn't know these were your vegetables.

69
00:03:42,200 --> 00:03:45,160
And why on earth are you starting
