70
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:46,880
It's Christopher!

71
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:48,840
He is not a vegetable.

72
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:52,840
You have no right to call him a vegetable.

73
00:03:53,640 --> 00:03:56,000
Christopher....

74
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:59,720
Then what exactly is Christopher?

75
00:03:59,720 --> 00:04:01,840
