80
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:09,440
He's into veggie skinship.

81
00:04:09,440 --> 00:04:11,000
Huh?

82
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:12,800
All-New...

83
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:15,320
No, gross!

84
00:04:15,320 --> 00:04:19,360
I just want someone to care about...

85
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:20,280
