86
00:04:20,280 --> 00:04:22,280
and to give love to...

87
00:04:23,760 --> 00:04:26,320
Shit, now that I say it out loud,
it really does sound like a veggie freak.

88
00:04:26,320 --> 00:04:27,560
But it's not like that.

89
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:29,360
When I'm with plants and vegetables...

90
00:04:29,360 --> 00:04:31,360
I feel more like myself.

91
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:34,080
They aren't like humans. Humans...

92
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:36,720
Humans are fickle.

93
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:40,040
Once you try to love them,
it just gives you a headache.

94
00:04:41,160 --> 00:04:42,840
Hey!

95
00:04:42,840 --> 00:04:44,160
See?

96
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:46,720
This is what happens
when you talk to humans.

97
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:48,640
Being with Christopher is...

98
00:04:48,640 --> 00:04:49,800
It's better.

99
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:52,000
That's why I like it.

100
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,280
I think this is getting weird.

101
00:04:53,280 --> 00:04:54,840
I bet he's...

102
00:04:54,840 --> 00:04:57,040
doing "something" with those veggies.

103
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:59,040
I'm just growing them!

104
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:02,680
He mentioned he got an A in Agriculture.

105
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:04,080
I got straight A's in every subject, man.

106
00:05:04,080 --> 00:05:05,800
He has a talent for this?

107
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:07,360
I have other talents too.

108
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:10,320
Maybe he was born for this?

109
00:05:10,320 --> 00:05:10,760
Look.

110
00:05:10,760 --> 00:05:12,720
No, I think actually...

111
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:14,800
