112
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:16,320
Let's get back to work.

113
00:05:18,880 --> 00:05:20,760
What genetics?

114
00:05:20,760 --> 00:05:21,760
Genetics.

115
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,000
Genetics.

116
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:27,360
Green-etics.

117
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:29,000
Genetics.

118
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:30,920
Greens...

119
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:35,920
Genetics, green-etics, DNA.

120
00:05:36,440 --> 00:05:38,840
Or maybe...

121
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:40,400
