122
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:43,680
Am I a plant?

123
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:47,480
Penelope, come here.
Hurry up.

124
00:05:48,160 --> 00:05:50,680
Go over there and film me.
Get my good side.

125
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:51,920
You're gorgeous.

126
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:54,440
I'm going to do a "sad" bit,
so don't you dare say I look pretty.

127
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:58,800
Goodbye, lavatory...

128
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:02,400
