129
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:05,760
Goodbye...

130
00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:07,440
This way, pan the camera, pan it!

131
00:06:07,440 --> 00:06:08,560
Goodbye...

132
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:12,440
The baby changing station tag,
which I'll never see again.

133
00:06:12,440 --> 00:06:14,320
Are the tears coming?

134
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:15,320
Film it, film it!

135
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,920
The cockpit.

136
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:21,120
This is as far as I can go to say goodbye.

137
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:22,120
Bye-bye.

138
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,720
Just kidding, guys!

139
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:28,760
An exclusive channel like mine
has to be extraordinary, right?

140
00:06:28,760 --> 00:06:31,360
So, let's go say our final goodbye
from the cockpit.

141
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:32,480
Follow me!

142
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:32,920
No!

143
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:33,800
What?

144
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:39,240
Video recording is strictly prohibited
in the cockpit under any circumstances.

145
00:06:40,960 --> 00:06:42,080
Why can't I go in?

146
00:06:42,080 --> 00:06:44,440
I'm just going in to take out the trash.

147
00:06:44,440 --> 00:06:46,560
The only trash I see right now...

148
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:49,040
