153
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:57,880
This content is going to be iconic.

154
00:06:57,880 --> 00:06:58,400
Come on!

155
00:06:58,720 --> 00:06:59,720
Come on!

156
00:07:00,880 --> 00:07:02,040
Here it is!

157
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:03,640
Are you blind?

158
00:07:03,640 --> 00:07:06,680
Can't you see this giant bag of trash?

159
00:07:06,840 --> 00:07:08,160
