165
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:19,640
Oh my god.

166
00:07:19,640 --> 00:07:22,280
That's not the right way to take a break.

167
00:07:22,280 --> 00:07:23,480
Wait here.

168
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:25,520
We aren't done yet, you and I.

169
00:07:25,520 --> 00:07:27,760
Go, go sit in First Class.
Go on, get up!

170
00:07:31,760 --> 00:07:35,000
So you're really not going to
let me into the cockpit?

171
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:35,880
No.

172
00:07:35,880 --> 00:07:38,920
Seriously, there's more to it than you think.

173
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:42,080
If you knew, you'd be stunned.

174
00:07:42,080 --> 00:07:45,880
Let me tell you something.
Do you want to know?

175
00:07:45,880 --> 00:07:47,560
I've wanted to talk about it for a long time.

176
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:50,680
But I'm not sure if I should say it.

177
00:07:51,520 --> 00:07:54,360
But honestly...I think I have to.

178
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:56,000
Oh my god!

179
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:57,560
So, do you actually know or not?

180
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:59,720
If you want me to tell you,
you need to listen carefully.

181
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:01,000
Are you going to listen?

182
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:01,960
I'm listening right now!

183
00:08:01,960 --> 00:08:04,480
But I'm not sure you're ready.

184
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:06,040
All in all...

185
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:07,320
Will you believe me?
That's all that matters.

186
00:08:07,320 --> 00:08:09,920
Oh my god,
if you don't know anything, then don't talk!

187
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:11,000
Just get out of my sight!

188
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:11,800
Get out of your sight? Anywhere?

189
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:12,600
Yes!

190
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:13,800
Fine then, I'm going into the cockpit.

191
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:15,440
Fine, do whatever you want!

192
00:08:15,440 --> 00:08:16,440
Thank you.

193
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:19,880
She just kept rambling on and on...

194
00:08:19,880 --> 00:08:21,760
Hey, no! Chaba, you can't!

195
00:08:24,200 --> 00:08:25,320
Captain!

196
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:27,760
First offi...

197
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:35,200
Chaba! You, bitch!

198
00:08:35,800 --> 00:08:39,720
Sky...our captain...our first officer...

199
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:40,840
where are they?

200
